{"tid":302014,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想養龜龜，求教","createTime":"2017-06-29T05:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T15:45:00.000Z","uid":15323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac6101d4fbd609a968c1b0df711bcb6ce6b0fde","tid":302014,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:17:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=%E8%98%87%E5%8D%A1%E9%81%94%E9%99%B8%E9%BE%9C&amp;safe=off&amp;rlz=1CDGOYI_enHK627HK627&amp;hl=en-GB&amp;prmd=inv&amp;source=lnms&amp;tbm=isch&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiN5ciPzODUAhUEnJQKHYZZCY0Q_AUICSgB&amp;biw=414&amp;bih=660\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%25E8%2598%2587%25E5%258D%25A1%25E9%2581%2594%25E9%2599%25B8%25E9%25BE%259C%26safe%3Doff%26rlz%3D1CDGOYI_enHK627HK627%26hl%3Den-GB%26prmd%3Dinv%26source%3Dlnms%26tbm%3Disch%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D0ahUKEwiN5ciPzODUAhUEnJQKHYZZCY0Q_AUICSgB%26biw%3D414%26bih%3D660&d=oER3DYiZ3pJIOgB8YS%2FshP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d096459e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=%E8%98%87%E5%8D%A1%E9%81%94%E9%99%B8%E9%BE%9C&amp;safe=off&amp;rlz=1CDGOYI_enHK627HK627&amp;hl=en-GB&amp;prmd=inv&amp;source=lnms&amp;tbm=isch&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiN5ciPzODUAhUEnJQKHYZZCY0Q_AUICSgB&amp;biw=414&amp;bih=660</a><br />\n<br />\n早幾日係旺角見到有呢種龜既bb買，要$9xx<br />\n見佢好得意好想養，想問下有咩要準備同注意架？<br />\n<br />\n伸 屋企有養開貓狗，並非三分鐘熱度"},{"pid":"00a00a6512e6aebc016950a988ce6b34faa81db0","tid":302014,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd84e803c6a8491d9c53c7aa8d112edfa2bfa2c","tid":302014,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T08:28:03.000Z","msg":"連登冇人養龜架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476a1c50946613d0e1bd60b2187e568d5e17eaa3","tid":302014,"uid":83439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T08:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=%E8%98%87%E5%8D%A1%E9%81%94%E9%99%B8%E9%BE%9C&amp;safe=off&amp;rlz=1CDGOYI_enHK627HK627&amp;hl=en-GB&amp;prmd=inv&amp;source=lnms&amp;tbm=isch&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiN5ciPzODUAhUEnJQKHYZZCY0Q_AUICSgB&amp;biw=414&amp;bih=660\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%25E8%2598%2587%25E5%258D%25A1%25E9%2581%2594%25E9%2599%25B8%25E9%25BE%259C%26safe%3Doff%26rlz%3D1CDGOYI_enHK627HK627%26hl%3Den-GB%26prmd%3Dinv%26source%3Dlnms%26tbm%3Disch%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D0ahUKEwiN5ciPzODUAhUEnJQKHYZZCY0Q_AUICSgB%26biw%3D414%26bih%3D660&d=oER3DYiZ3pJIOgB8YS%2FshP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d096459e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=%E8%98%87%E5%8D%A1%E9%81%94%E9%99%B8%E9%BE%9C&amp;safe=off&amp;rlz=1CDGOYI_enHK627HK627&amp;hl=en-GB&amp;prmd=inv&amp;source=lnms&amp;tbm=isch&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiN5ciPzODUAhUEnJQKHYZZCY0Q_AUICSgB&amp;biw=414&amp;bih=660</a><br />\n<br />\n早幾日係旺角見到有呢種龜既bb買，要$9xx<br />\n見佢好得意好想養，想問下有咩要準備同注意架？<br />\n<br />\n伸 屋企有養開貓狗，並非三分鐘熱度</blockquote><br />\n盾臂，自己google la"},{"pid":"b5ae11a8d92c79ecc8f8301c8f2c5c19f59a71f3","tid":302014,"uid":12208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T10:49:44.000Z","msg":"首先你屋企可以比到幾多位佢<br />\n我無記錯既盾臂體型陸龜中排第三<br />\n如果你諗住養到咁上下就轉手當我無講過<br />\n養陸龜同變色龍一樣<br />\n設備行先 齊晒所有野最後先到龜<br />\n飼養箱 uvb&amp;uva燈 水盆 底材（草粒樹皮之類）<br />\n仲有養得陸龜預左冬天電費增加<br />\n食既方面已經有陸龜糧 可以餵啲菜同生果<br />\n我都唔係好清楚 話說你直接問鋪頭會仲詳細<br />\n<br />\n利申：未養過陸龜"},{"pid":"d7c235ab40581575ce14ad05207d2a3ffbd14f1d","tid":302014,"uid":124958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T12:55:46.000Z","msg":"買龜千祈唔好係魚街買, 一係去魚佬, 一係去稀鰭<br />\n地址係邊自己搵"},{"pid":"5eadedd52cc9bb64844ef8e6c927c3cf2794653c","tid":302014,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T16:46:32.000Z","msg":"收到，唔該晒巴打<br />\n就算佢大得好快屋企都有地方比佢遊走<br />\ngoogle左好耐，而家只係諗緊d設備係邊買好<br />\n見淘寶都有但唔知用唔用得過<br />\n<br />\n另外我見d人話陸龜好容易生腎石，到底係咩一回事<br />\n因為養寵物一樣就好上心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 擔心佢好易病養唔大"},{"pid":"0d5b07f7b77e880de28f7964d22888dbd849e95e","tid":302014,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T16:47:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收到，唔該晒巴打<br />\n就算佢大得好快屋企都有地方比佢遊走<br />\ngoogle左好耐，而家只係諗緊d設備係邊買好<br />\n見淘寶都有但唔知用唔用得過<br />\n<br />\n另外我見d人話陸龜好容易生腎石，到底係咩一回事<br />\n因為養寵物一<span style=\"color: red;\">養</span>就好上心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 擔心佢好易病養唔大</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7e66566c95a374e1d2186f4c455d456b8c8937d1","tid":302014,"uid":23871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T16:48:13.000Z","msg":"陸龜難養過水龜 好容易有肺炎"},{"pid":"4ad7e9cbbe4b92dadb5b1cf27a42642a5985d8bb","tid":302014,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T16:53:29.000Z","msg":"我只會建議有天台/花園，照到太陽光既人養"},{"pid":"598d1598281114d439536d3fe13e40f734b9bb4b","tid":302014,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T17:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我只會建議有天台/花園，照到太陽光既人養</blockquote><br />\n有好大地方係可以曬到陽光<br />\n而家係膽心佢易唔易有腎石同應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外應該去邊買龜好，香港只識旺角..."},{"pid":"248aaae007acd6b9952b55bcdf83ea908f3708e6","tid":302014,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T19:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收到，唔該晒巴打<br />\n就算佢大得好快屋企都有地方比佢遊走<br />\ngoogle左好耐，而家只係諗緊d設備係邊買好<br />\n見淘寶都有但唔知用唔用得過<br />\n<br />\n另外我見d人話陸龜好容易生腎石，到底係咩一回事<br />\n因為養寵物一樣就好上心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 擔心佢好易病養唔大</blockquote><br />\n陸龜係易有腎石<br />\n因為攝水唔夠引致<br />\n<br />\n其實每款龜種最基本嘅資料可係香港兩棲及爬蟲協會搵到<br />\ngoogle: （龜嘅種類） 香港兩棲及爬蟲協會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中非陸龜/ 盾臂陸龜/ 蘇卡達陸龜 - 香港兩棲及爬蟲協會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.hkherp.org/document/caresheet/Geochelone_sulcata.pdf&amp;ved=0ahUKEwihkd6a4ePUAhWGFpQKHXexD50QFghGMAs&amp;usg=AFQjCNEQ0hzoiyOz-GjU72DNILqtWif9Tg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkherp.org%2Fdocument%2Fcaresheet%2FGeochelone_sulcata.pdf%26ved%3D0ahUKEwihkd6a4ePUAhWGFpQKHXexD50QFghGMAs%26usg%3DAFQjCNEQ0hzoiyOz-GjU72DNILqtWif9Tg&d=oER3DYiZ3pJIOgB8YS%2FshP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4057e348\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.hkherp.org/document/caresheet/Geochelone_sulcata.pdf&amp;ved=0ahUKEwihkd6a4ePUAhWGFpQKHXexD50QFghGMAs&amp;usg=AFQjCNEQ0hzoiyOz-GjU72DNILqtWif9Tg</a>"},{"pid":"7592ffa3b080b21a3440ecc2536d2a6bc566f389","tid":302014,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T19:18:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>收到，唔該晒巴打<br />\n就算佢大得好快屋企都有地方比佢遊走<br />\ngoogle左好耐，而家只係諗緊d設備係邊買好<br />\n見淘寶都有但唔知用唔用得過<br />\n<br />\n另外我見d人話陸龜好容易生腎石，到底係咩一回事<br />\n因為養寵物一樣就好上心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 擔心佢好易病養唔大</blockquote><br />\n陸龜係易有腎石<br />\n因為攝水唔夠引致<br />\n<br />\n其實每款龜種最基本嘅資料可係香港兩棲及爬蟲協會搵到<br />\ngoogle: （龜嘅種類） 香港兩棲及爬蟲協會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中非陸龜/ 盾臂陸龜/ 蘇卡達陸龜 - 香港兩棲及爬蟲協會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.hkherp.org/document/caresheet/Geochelone_sulcata.pdf&amp;ved=0ahUKEwihkd6a4ePUAhWGFpQKHXexD50QFghGMAs&amp;usg=AFQjCNEQ0hzoiyOz-GjU72DNILqtWif9Tg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkherp.org%2Fdocument%2Fcaresheet%2FGeochelone_sulcata.pdf%26ved%3D0ahUKEwihkd6a4ePUAhWGFpQKHXexD50QFghGMAs%26usg%3DAFQjCNEQ0hzoiyOz-GjU72DNILqtWif9Tg&d=oER3DYiZ3pJIOgB8YS%2FshP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4057e348\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.hkherp.org/document/caresheet/Geochelone_sulcata.pdf&amp;ved=0ahUKEwihkd6a4ePUAhWGFpQKHXexD50QFghGMAs&amp;usg=AFQjCNEQ0hzoiyOz-GjU72DNILqtWif9Tg</a></blockquote><br />\n貼唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主自己Google「盾臂龜 香港兩棲及爬蟲協會」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d294cc7fe43f0479bb9e88b2762d5dede2430af","tid":302014,"uid":122824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T20:07:43.000Z","msg":"d龜好臭"},{"pid":"4c453e025f91160c18249b4e5c26cb537a41d4d6","tid":302014,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:18:11.000Z","msg":"有宜間，有太陽，定期浸水，應該唔大問題<br />\n反而買大隻少少（2-3000蚊），你講900蚊個啲應該好細隻"},{"pid":"1872d4b872aec430dc117ff20c95c18ce6d206e6","tid":302014,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:42:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有宜間，有太陽，定期浸水，應該唔大問題<br />\n反而買大隻少少（2-3000蚊），你講900蚊個啲應該好細隻</blockquote><br />\n諗住養寵物由細養起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但我都知佢好難養得大<br />\n所以諗住做好十成準備先買龜龜"},{"pid":"eaa0eff4d2b0baba54a42985bd218ac269e7bb1a","tid":302014,"uid":83759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:58:40.000Z","msg":"最緊要有空間 <br />\n盾臂龜算容易養<br />\n唔好餵咁多高水份菜 <br />\n主食草 <br />\n就無事"},{"pid":"9a435b25e7b1db9c16ff8ccd7984e3d7928a6a68","tid":302014,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:27:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最緊要有空間 <br />\n盾臂龜算容易養<br />\n唔好餵咁多高水份菜 <br />\n主食草 <br />\n就無事</blockquote><br />\n巴打你都係養盾臂？其實香港邊度買龜信譽好d"},{"pid":"017d478e8cfe65c4035cf5e16544742c6c435fa2","tid":302014,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:08:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>收到，唔該晒巴打<br />\n就算佢大得好快屋企都有地方比佢遊走<br />\ngoogle左好耐，而家只係諗緊d設備係邊買好<br />\n見淘寶都有但唔知用唔用得過<br />\n<br />\n另外我見d人話陸龜好容易生腎石，到底係咩一回事<br />\n因為養寵物一樣就好上心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 擔心佢好易病養唔大</blockquote><br />\n陸龜係易有腎石<br />\n因為攝水唔夠引致<br />\n<br />\n其實每款龜種最基本嘅資料可係香港兩棲及爬蟲協會搵到<br />\ngoogle: （龜嘅種類） 香港兩棲及爬蟲協會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中非陸龜/ 盾臂陸龜/ 蘇卡達陸龜 - 香港兩棲及爬蟲協會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.hkherp.org/document/caresheet/Geochelone_sulcata.pdf&amp;ved=0ahUKEwihkd6a4ePUAhWGFpQKHXexD50QFghGMAs&amp;usg=AFQjCNEQ0hzoiyOz-GjU72DNILqtWif9Tg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkherp.org%2Fdocument%2Fcaresheet%2FGeochelone_sulcata.pdf%26ved%3D0ahUKEwihkd6a4ePUAhWGFpQKHXexD50QFghGMAs%26usg%3DAFQjCNEQ0hzoiyOz-GjU72DNILqtWif9Tg&d=oER3DYiZ3pJIOgB8YS%2FshP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4057e348\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.hkherp.org/document/caresheet/Geochelone_sulcata.pdf&amp;ved=0ahUKEwihkd6a4ePUAhWGFpQKHXexD50QFghGMAs&amp;usg=AFQjCNEQ0hzoiyOz-GjU72DNILqtWif9Tg</a></blockquote><br />\n貼唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主自己Google「盾臂龜 香港兩棲及爬蟲協會」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已睇過晒，但巴打們有冇咩買龜龜係有信譽d架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ngoogle過晒都冇，d人話唔好去金魚街咋"},{"pid":"47f34d5d432f975513fa59633c68c43aeaf6b01c","tid":302014,"uid":79126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:10:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有宜間，有太陽，定期浸水，應該唔大問題<br />\n反而買大隻少少（2-3000蚊），你講900蚊個啲應該好細隻</blockquote><br />\n諗住養寵物由細養起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但我都知佢好難養得大<br />\n所以諗住做好十成準備先買龜龜</blockquote><br />\n你做足十成準備都好，咁細隻個d係好易死"},{"pid":"209a4d7673dcc0531d1a7ccbc3976be9b9763bf3","tid":302014,"uid":79126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:11:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><bl